profile:
Nothing brings a living space together better than the warmth and glow of a beautifully crafted fireplace. Especially during Stayner’s cold winters, a well functioning fireplace is essential for heating your home. Our Stayner fireplace experts can help you bring your dream fireplace to life, all while ensuring heating efficiency is maximized for your home. Whether you are into bolder styles or something more classic, Fireplace Family has got you covered. We offer installations of gas fireplaces, wood fireplaces, and electric fireplaces, and our experts are always available to assist you in choosing the best option for your home’s heating needs. No matter how big or small the project, our fireplace experts can help you build the fireplace of your dreams!

In addition to installations, Fireplace Family offers fireplace repair services to make sure that your fireplace is functioning as it should. Whether it’s a gas fireplace, wood fireplace, or electric fireplace that needs repairing, our experts will see to it that your fireplace is running again in prime condition.
